payload.description: .files, including ~/.osx — sensible hacker defaults for OS X

commits.message:
Update .macos

Update with options from upstream

Update .gitconfig

Update with latest from upstream

Create autohotkey_home_end.ahk

Maps Ctrl+Right/Left to End/Home to emulate Mac bindings

Update .ideavimrc_win

Add note about ^P and ^N popup navigation

Update .ideavimrc

Add note about ^P and ^N navigation for popup menus

Update .ideavimrc

Remove popup navigation in favor of IDE ^P and ^N

Update .ideavimrc_win

Remove popup navigation in favor of IDE ^P and ^N
